\c 48 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 48\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Xiyoon, Tulluu Isa Mandara Waaqayyoo Keessaa (Weedduu; faarfannaa ilmaan Qoraahi)
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo guddaa dha, mandara isaa keessatti tulluu isa qulqullaa'aa irrattis guddisee kan jajamuu dha.
\m \bd 2\bd* Tulluun Xiyoon inni ol ka'inni isaa miidhagaan, guutummaa lafa kanaaf gammachuu dha; inni mandara mootii guddichaa keessaa, gara bitaatti ol fagaatee jira.
\m \bd 3\bd* Mana ishee warra jajjaboo keessatti Waaqayyo ofii isaatii, da'oo amanamaa isheedhaaf ta'uu isaa mul'iseera.
\m \bd 4\bd* Kunoo, mootonni walitti in qabaman, wal duukaas itti in adeeman.
\m \bd 5\bd* Akkuma kana arganiin na'anii in dinqifatan, wareeranii baqa keessaa fuudhan.
\m \bd 6\bd* Achitti rom'uun isaanitti dhufe, akka dubartii da'uuf ciniinsifatus muddamni isaan in qabate.
\m \bd 7\bd* Akka markaboota gara buufata Tarshiishitti adeemanii, warra qilleensa gara ba'a-biiftuutiin hurreeffamanii in ta'an. 
\m \bd 8\bd* Waaqayyo bara baraan mandara isaa jabeessee akka dhaabu, akkuma dhageenye akkasumas mandara gooftaa maccaa, isa kan Waaqayyo keenyaa irratti argineerra.
\m \bd 9\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, mana qulqullummaa kee keessatti, nuyi gaarummaa kee yaadanneerra.
\m \bd 10\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, akkuma maqaan kee fagoo ga'e, jajuun kees andaara lafaa in ga'a; harka kee mirgaa keessa qajeelinni guuteera.
\m \bd 11\bd* Firdii dhugaa ati laattuuf tulluun Xiyoon haa gammadu, mandaroonni Yihudaas haa ililchan.
\m \bd 12\bd* Mandara Xiyoon naanna'aa, ishees marsaa, riqaa dhagaa ishee keessatti ijaaramanis lakkaa'aa.
\m \bd 13\bd* Dhaloota dhufutti akka himtaniifis dallaa ishee yaadaan qabaa, mana ishee warra jajjaboo keessa adeemaa!
\m \bd 14\bd* Inni kun Waaqayyo akka ta'e, yeroo hundumaa bara baraan Waaqayyo keenya, ammaa hamma du'a garasiittis geggeessaa keenya ta'uu isaa himaa!
\b 
